*Ostati* će da se čuva u sefu. (It will remain in the safe.)

*Ostala* je zaprepašćena. (She was shocked.)

*Ostaće* da se čuva tajna. (The secret will remain.)

*Ostala* je u šoku. (She remained in shock.)

*Ostaju* nam još dva dana. (We have two more days left.)

*Ostali* smo bez hrane. (We stayed without food.)

*Ostati* će da traje dugo. (It will remain for a long time.)

*Ostale* su bez odgovora. (They were left without answers.)

*Ostanu* im još neke stvari da se obave. (They still have some things to do.)

*Ostane* još jedna stvar za završiti. (One more thing will remain to be finished.)